reviews.review_text: Nice Upgrade Sounds great, thank you.

underlooked? i find the fact that there is only one prior review of this copy to be confusing. the sound quality of this show could easily be one of the best from the early 70's. unbelievable china>rider, where the rider has tiny hints and teases of the melody from china cat. one of my favorite shows from '71.
How has it been over a decade 11 years and no comments? This is incredible sound quality. Best you’re gonna get from early 70’s. Almost sounds as good as a modern show release at the cap.
